This is not a single road as shown on the map, but two separate roads which terminate at the map marker location. There is a residence inbetween that blocks the two roads.  This link has negative consequences for routing - access to Abeyratne Mawatha is easier through this (nonexistent) through road, so OSM based routing products tend to recommend it, while in reality no such throughfare exists.

There is an unpaved track which runs parallel to Ambillawatte Road for about 70-80 metres and then does a 90 degree turn to run parallel to 20th Lane, starting from the map marker. This track is visible on satellite view, and has 10-15 vehicles traveling on a daily basis - from the residences at the end of the track, and also from a welding and grill work business.  This used to be on OSM at one point, but was removed. Access from the residences/businesses to the main road is via Pirivena Road

opening_comment: A Ride in to the Nature... with the team of Hikkaduwa Lagoon Safari  Dodandoowa Lagoon & Polgasduwa Hermitage , Hikkaduwa  A eco friendly & peaceful catamaran boat safari around  Dodanduwa lake,Hikkaduwa would be marvelous experience for travellers who love nature & calmness .  In the middle of Dodanduwa lake, there are several islands and the biggest one is the Polgasduwa, which is world famous for century old forest hermitage. Thousands of birds are living on the trees in small islands. Evening boat rides are fortunate to see birds flying their nests over water in dusk. Fish therapy will be a true treat for your foots and keep your nerves awake.   Excursions on traditional restored Catamarans will be a true experience for the adventurous traveller. Bird watching and a visit to the local cinnamon factory and island will be another pleasure traveller may indulge in while on Dodanduwa lake safari. Also you can visit Ancient buddhist temple near by catamaran boat. Lovers of photography can spend long hours capturing the colourful beauty of the sunset.   Man powered boats like Catamarans helps to keep true beauty to next generation with a minimal impact to nature.   Dodanduwa Lagoon Safari is  one of the best eco travel experience which you can do around Hikkaduwa & Southern. (OSM data version: 2016-06-20T05:57:02Z) #mapsme
